For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO ALLOW A COURT TO WAIVE CERTAIN FEES WHEN A
10 JUVENILE IS ORDERED TO REGISTER AS A SEX OFFENDER;
11 AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
